{"tid":377100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"多部份澳門人中晒斯德哥爾摩綜合症","createTime":"2017-08-27T13:21:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T04:24:05.000Z","uid":67043,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"52796cce555a4789e3a88a16558793e7d87373d5","tid":377100,"uid":67043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T13:21:47.000Z","msg":"斯德哥爾摩綜合症：是一種心理學現象，是指犯罪的被害者對於加害者產生情感、同情加害者<br />\n<br />\n呢次災難明顯係澳共政權既無能導致<br />\n解放軍出黎幫手只係為咗贖罪<br />\n但你哋就感動晒流晒馬尿咁做咩姐<br />\n你估澳門依家個政府咁無能，中共係無份既咩？<br />\n<br />\n澳門人最需要多謝既係個班義工，<br />\n佢哋冇糧出，冇人命令，純自發去做<br />\n得到既掌聲反而比解放軍少，真係攪笑"},{"pid":"902d6da3bc3a91808de5f84926aaf82e29330f3e","tid":377100,"uid":127569,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T14:04:33.000Z","msg":"澳門狗有腦就唔會搞到今時今日咁既田地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af826d29940835d18c3f16284028ef3b34c57e4b","tid":377100,"uid":137627,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T14:08:08.000Z","msg":"政府應該做就唔做，全澳市民自發性清理，最終老解出埸半日將功勞立晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec684ff64a40bb26a101263731613493fab4bb74","tid":377100,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T14:25:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eaaf43c9832253769db7d7ab4814a4867adb0ac","tid":377100,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T14:25:56.000Z","msg":"華生"},{"pid":"93b7192c7a741a5671873fd29c45087e4b8e0311","tid":377100,"uid":27664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T14:28:57.000Z","msg":"支澳政府公布仲話市民啲大型垃圾放係街咗尻住支解軍做野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b049aa89c2f363ad059ef10b75d7d4041ab24e03","tid":377100,"uid":4783,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3